description:
                Importer and Exporter for Vienna energy files. Allows
                converting Turner parameter files to Vienna parameter files.
                .
                This is the 2011 post-library split version, hence not
                deprecated anymore.



extra-source-files:
  parfiles/rna_turner2004.par



library
  build-depends:
    base >3 && <5,
